member.example:
The following example shows how a root  can be instructed to temporarily
apply a  to its background, while a dialog is being shown on top of
the blurred background.


    var owner = Window.GetWindow(this);
    var root = owner.GetRoot();
    BackgroundBlurBehavior.SetBackgroundBlur(root, true);
    var dialog = new Dialog { Owner = owner };
    dialog.ShowDialog();
    BackgroundBlurBehavior.SetBackgroundBlur(root, false);

